node.text: Esther Povitsky of @cw_crazyxgf, @alonetogethertv, @dollfaceonhulu, and her new @comedycentral special ‘Hot For My Name’ was set up with @elitedaily’s in-house astrologer @valeriemesa for a full birth chart reading. As a Pisces ♓️ sun, Leo ♌️ moon, and Sagittarius ♐️ rising, there was *a lot* to unpack. Check out the full reading and @esthermonster’s reaction 🔮

node.title: Esther Povitsky Gets Her Birth Chart Read

node.text: Just because we can’t congregate in the streets doesn’t mean that we can't show off our pride in 2020 🌈 RuPaul’s All Star season 5 cast @blairst.clair, @indiaferrah, @miss_alexis_mateo, @derrickbarry, @jujubeeonline, @mug4dayz, @theonlymayhem, @miz_cracker, @sheacoulee and Ongina are here to serve up some inspiration with their loud and proud outfits and messages for the pride season.

node.title: RuPaul’s Drag Race All Stars Celebrate Virtual Pride

node.text: For TikTok LGBTQ+ Trailblazer Cristian Dennis acceptance has been a journey. For those who struggle with their identity, he encourages one thing: patience. Follow @cristiandennis on TikTok for more! #mypride

node.title: Pride From Home With TikTok Trailblazer CristianDennis

node.text:
NCT 127 has had their hands full this past year, and on the group’s fifth anniversary earlier this week, they announced their highly anticipated next album will be released this September. While NCTzens don’t know much about #NCT’s upcoming project yet, the group opened up about what they’ve been doing outside of rehearsing that even die-hard fans will be surprised to learn about.

At the link in bio, @michmendezmedia speaks with @nct127 members Johnny, Haechan, Mark, Taeyong, Jaehyun, Yuta, Taeil, Jungwoo, and Doyoung about their lives outside of music and the interests they’ve been obsessing over in their down time. #nct127
